				<h1>Welcome</h1>
				<p>Sheffield and District Landlord Association (SADLA) is
				 a non-profit making organisation of private landlords providing a united front to represent their interests.</p>
				<p>SADLA are affiliated to the <a href="http://www.landlords.org.uk/"
        			target="_blank">National Landlords Association</a>&nbsp;<img src="/images/exlink.gif">&nbsp; (NLA). 
                  	This is the only nationally recognised body of residential landlords 
                  	which is consulted by the Government, Judiciary and Media.</p>
				<p>Our <a href="benefits.asp">membership</a> covers all types 
                  	of landlord no matter how large or small their portfolio. <a href="join.asp">Join</a> 
                  	SADLA and help develop the Association in a way that can benefit 
                  	your business. </p>

