					<a name="news"></a> <div class="newsitem"><h2>With great sadness we have to announce the death of Stuart Simcock our treasurer and secretary
		</h2>
		

<p>Stuart Simcock passed away very suddenly&nbsp;last night. He was both&nbsp;the secretary and Treasurer of the association, and the committee will miss him dearly. Stuart has dedicated his semi retirement to the work of the association and&nbsp;we have all&nbsp;appreciated the tremendous contribution he has made.</p><p style="text-align:right"><a href="newsitem.asp?id=64&f=/default.asp">Read More...</a></p></div>  <div class="newsitem"><h2>
			<span style="float:right;color:#888; font-size:70%;">05/04/2009</span>
